!!二分法とNewton法のコード


!!二分法(bisection) 
<<<maple
> x1:=0: x2:=0.8: 
  f1:=func(x1): f2:=func(x2): 
  for i from 1 to 5 do 
    x:=(x1+x2)/2;
    f:=func(x); 
    if f*f1>=0.0 then 
      x1:=x; f1:=f; 
    else 
      x2:=x; f2:=f; 
    end if;
    printf("%20.15f, %20.15f\n",x,f); 
  end do:
>>>
